steps.name: When the user logs in with valid credentials
And the user is redirected to the dashboard
When the user navigates to the coaches page and selects a "Henry"
And the user selects a workout for the date and time "08:00 - 09:00 AM"
And the user clicks on the book workout button
Then the workout is booked successfully with a toast message "Workout booked successfully!"
When the user navigates to the workouts page
And the user clicks the finish workout button
And the user provides a rating 5 and feedback "Great workout! Felt relaxed and energized."
Then the workout rating and feedback is successfully submitted with message "Feedback submitted successfully"

parameters.name: feedback
parameters.value: Great workout! Felt relaxed and energized.
